================================================================================
ADDITIONAL NOTICE — RESEARCH SOFTWARE, NOT FOR PRODUCTION USE
================================================================================

This software is a research reference implementation accompanying an academic
paper on bonded sub-satoshi channels for Bitcoin SV (post-Genesis). It is
designed and tested only in regtest (a self-contained local development
network). It MUST NOT be connected to mainnet or used to custody real funds.

By default the embedded node runs in regtest mode. A `--mainnet` flag is
provided only so independent review can verify that mainnet operation is
explicitly opt-in and gated behind interactive confirmation; supplying it for
any other purpose is unsupported and at the user's own risk.

The authors make no representation that this implementation is fit for any
production deployment, payment processing, or storage of value.
